Netropolitan Avenne, at the N.E. corner of Sixty-ninth Avenue, showirg in three views the home of Col. Hunt. Cwners of this property and house were Thomas Hunt, 1860-'3; J. Hunt, 1891; Hunt -state, 1896; Yhomas Hunt, 19U9; and the Pennsylvania Hailroad in 1923. One Wolfert was the occupant in 1922. TRe house was demolished in February 1925. View No. 3 is a side view of the house.
